title: NOM - No Other Meaning at Macpherson Community Club
blurb: Visit NOM at Macpherson Community Club Level 1!
description: NOM offers a variety of dining options in a family-friendly environment. Enjoy our menu selections during our opening hours. We are located at Macpherson Community Club, Level 1. Our operating hours are weekdays 12pm-10pm and Sat/Sun/Public Holidays 11am-10pm. We are closed every Tuesday. If PH falls on a Tuesday, we will be closed on Wednesday instead. Contact us at +65 6747 3839 or info@noothermeaning.com for inquiries.
full_address: 400 Paya Lebar Way, Macpherson Community Club Level 1, Singapore 379131
